        {
            "title": "貝森特稱中國正以「完美節奏」完成今年大豆採購目標",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國財政部長斯科特·貝森特周三表示，中國正向著在2月底前購買1200萬噸美國大豆的方向邁進。這個說法似乎延長了此前設定的採購最後期限。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">白宮上個月曾表示，中國已同意在「2025年最後兩個月」採購上述數量的大豆。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">貝森特在《紐約時報》舉辦的活動上接受採訪時說：「我要說的是，中國正在按計畫履行協議的每一部分，協議的每一部分。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">當被問及大豆採購進度以及距離年底還有多少時間時，他澄清說，目標是「季末，所以我認為應該是2月28日」。美國大豆的銷售年度是從9月到次年8月。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-08952db8-b5de-34dc-9212-f72a2bbdb67d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「他們正以完美的節奏完成這個目標。」他說，「從裝載量來看，他們中央政府的採購節奏也完全符合預期。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：貿易商稱中國仍有望實現今年採購美國大豆的承諾目標</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">就在一個多月前，中國領導人習近平在韓國與美國總統唐川普會晤後，中國承諾今年至少購買1200萬噸大豆，未來三年每年至少再採購2500萬噸。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Bessent Says China 「in a Perfect Cadence」 to Meet Soy Target</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%9D%E6%A3%AE%E7%89%B9%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%A3%E4%BB%A5-%E5%AE%8C%E7%BE%8E%E7%AF%80%E5%A5%8F-%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E5%A4%A7%E8%B1%86%E6%8E%A1%E8%B3%BC%E7%9B%AE%E6%A8%99-051223517.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-04 13:50:54",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "宗馥莉尋求就香港滙豐賬戶18億美元資產進一步上訴",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 中國飲料巨頭杭州娃哈哈集團的繼承人<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:宗馥莉;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/宗馥莉\">宗馥莉</a>正在尋求法院批准，就涉及在香港滙豐賬戶中18億美元資產的兩項判令提起進一步上訴。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據彭博新聞社查閱的法庭文件顯示，宗馥莉已向上訴法院申請許可，對高等法院此前頒布的資產保全令及披露令發起挑戰。文件顯示，她請求法院撤銷這兩項命令並駁回原訴傳票。宗馥莉與三位同父異母的兄弟姐妹正陷於遺產糾紛。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這是宗馥莉為推翻訴訟中的判令而做出的最新努力。這一訴訟案已在國內引發熱議，並成為財富保全和家族糾紛討論的焦點。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-1d2d5fbd-0aea-345b-8bac-eb63c00d0ed5-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據法庭文件，宗馥莉的律師列出了上訴的五個主要理由，認為原告——宗繼昌、宗婕莉和宗繼盛——對滙豐賬戶資產缺乏強有力的所有權；不存在流失的風險；以及之前的法官未能確定原告在滙豐賬戶中有什麼權益。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Beverage Heiress Seeks Further Appeal for $1.8 Billion Assets</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%AE%97%E9%A6%A5%E8%8E%89%E5%B0%8B%E6%B1%82%E5%B0%B1%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90%E8%B3%AC%E6%88%B618%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E8%B3%87%E7%94%A2%E9%80%B2-%E6%AD%A5%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4-041453124.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-04 13:00:49",
